So it's a great honor for me and pleasure to

3
00:00:17.520 --> 00:00:18.680
chair this session and

4
00:00:20.300 --> 00:00:22.560
invite these fantastic speakers.

5
00:00:23.230 --> 00:00:27.040
We're going to be discussing the microbiome with relation to CAR

6
00:00:27.080 --> 00:00:30.320
T cell therapy, and I think a little bit more broadly to

7
00:00:30.360 --> 00:00:34.280
immunotherapy as well. I have just a few intro slides

8
00:00:34.340 --> 00:00:37.020
