211
00:12:58.400 --> 00:13:02.060
So in summary, anaerobic antibiotics

212
00:13:02.420 --> 00:13:06.220
may influence CAR T cell therapy by altering the intestinal microbiome.

213
00:13:06.280 --> 00:13:08.880
We hypothesize that these antibiotics

214
00:13:09.760 --> 00:13:13.420
